      "excerpt": "Vancouver Island was nothing short of an adventure, a stunning mix of natural beauty and wildlife encounters that we'll remember for a long time. The weather was absolutely perfect throughout the trip, making it so easy to explore and soak in the great outdoors. We picked a lovely campsite close to Tofino that felt just right, serving as our cozy home base for all the exploration we had planned.",
