    "data": {
      "title": "Copenhagen",
      "slug": "2024-09-18-copenhagen",
      "date": "2024-09-18",
      "author": "Stefan",
      "excerpt": "Copenhagen is a beautiful city with lots of interesting and nice architecture. We were especially blown away by the cycling infrastructure. We had heard it's a ‚Äúbike city‚Äù, but we had no idea just how fantastic it is to explore the city by bike. I have probably never felt this safe and respected as a cyclist.",
      "categories": [
        "üá©üá∞ Denmark",
        "üöê Van life",
        "üåÖ On the road"
      ],
      "heroImage": "/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240915_124444.jpeg",
      "heroImageAlt": "View of a church close to the Fort in Copenhagen.",
      "status": "published"
    },
    "content": "\nCopenhagen is a beautiful city with lots of interesting and nice architecture. We were especially blown away by the cycling infrastructure. We had heard it's a ‚Äúbike city‚Äù, but we had no idea just how fantastic it is to explore the city by bike. I have probably never felt this safe and respected as a cyclist.\n\nWe took it easy and just let ourselves go with the flow‚Ä¶\n\n:::gallery\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240915_124444.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240915_125324.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240915_130104.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240915_131808.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240914_181038.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240914_185734.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240915_122027.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240915_132123.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240915_143308.jpeg\n:::\n\n## Dinner at ARK\n\n[ARK](https://www.restaurantark.dk/eat) is a ‚Äúgreen Michelin star‚Äù restaurant with a focus on sustainability and it is 100% vegan.\n\nIt was probably the best food we ever experienced and the waiters were amazing, too! They were knowledgeable and fun, but also knew when to just let people enjoy their food.\n\nIt was mindblowing! We also had the wine selection and that in itself was great.\n\nHere are some impressions of the menu.\n\n:::gallery\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240918_183654.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240918_184723.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240918_194202.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240918_192011.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240918_201226.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240918_190135.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240918_204904.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240918_211054.jpeg\n/images/road-trips/denmark-2024/IMG_20240918_213933.jpeg\n:::\n",
