      "excerpt": "After visiting Reine and the tiny village of √Ö at the very end of the road, we continued our journey to Vikten ‚Äì a small and peaceful place known for its glass workshop and its stunning beach. \nThe light there was absolutely magical. Soft, golden, and constantly changing, it turned the whole landscape into a painting. A group of photographers had gathered to capture the scenery, and we completely understood why.",
